---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import TextTransformer from '@/components/TextTransformer';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Glitch Text Generator" 
  description="Create corrupted, zalgo, and glitched text effects with our free glitch text generator"
>
  <TextTransformer 
    client:load
    title="Glitch Text Generator" 
    description="Transform your text into corrupted, glitched, and zalgo effects" 
    transformType="glitch"
    placeholder="Enter your text to create glitch effects..."
  />

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">About Glitch Text Generator</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <p>The Glitch Text Generator creates various corrupted and distorted text effects that simulate digital glitches, zalgo text, and other creepy or broken text styles.</p>
          <p>These effects use Unicode combining characters and special symbols to create the appearance of corrupted or glitched text that works across most platforms.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">Glitch Effects Available</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Random Character Glitch:</strong> Replaces some characters with random symbols</li>
            <li><strong>Zalgo Text:</strong> Adds combining characters above, below, and through text</li>
            <li><strong>Strikethrough Glitch:</strong> Adds strikethrough effects to all characters</li>
            <li><strong>Double Vision:</strong> Duplicates each character for a double vision effect</li>
            <li><strong>Inverted Characters:</strong> Flips characters upside down</li>
            <li><strong>Bracketed Glitch:</strong> Randomly adds brackets around characters</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">Perfect for</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Horror and creepy content</li>
            <li>Gaming usernames and profiles</li>
            <li>Digital art and design projects</li>
            <li>Social media posts with edgy aesthetics</li>
            <li>Creative writing and storytelling</li>
            <li>Cyberpunk and tech-themed content</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">Note: Some glitch effects may not display correctly on all devices or platforms, especially older systems with limited Unicode support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
